{"tid":834470,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞周三推特濃版黑椒漢堡 龍蝦湯味 Shake Shake 薯條同步登場","createTime":"2018-09-24T08:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T11:22:27.000Z","uid":39628,"like":51,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"35d0a9ac486496f8478e7d00d078383cc1b1db3d","tid":834470,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"各位麥當勞 fans 又有食好西的理由了！事關麥當勞由 9 月 26 日星期三，上午 11 時後開始會將經典好西黑椒漢堡，化身特濃版黑椒漢堡和脆脆黑椒漢堡登場！同場亦會新推大大杯青蘋果梳打茶，以及龍蝦湯味 Shake Shake 調味粉，讓大家製作最惹味的邪惡版薯條，吃到欲罷不能，就是如此<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2165000/2167508/20180924_mcd_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2165000%2F2167508%2F20180924_mcd_02_600.jpg&h=0662f859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，特濃版黑椒漢堡和脆脆黑椒漢堡的出現，意味上月推出的玉子將軍漢堡及將軍漢堡，即將再度跟大家講再見。之不過，喜歡牛肉及重口味的朋友，相信會更期待特濃版黑椒漢堡和脆脆黑椒漢堡的，只因當中黑椒味的勁度，的確有讓人一吃難忘的潛力，有興趣的朋友切勿錯過！<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，麥當勞由 9 月 26 日星期三開始，也會加推龍蝦湯味 Shake Shake 調味粉及大大杯青蘋果梳打茶。雖知道龍蝦湯味 Shake Shake 調味粉會是濃味之選，所以喝個味道清新的青蘋果梳打茶，應能作出調和之外，也夠解渴。提提大家，Shake Shake 薯條、大大杯青蘋果梳打茶的供應地點，是不包括沙田馬場及跑馬地馬場的麥當勞分店的，至於特濃版黑椒漢堡和脆脆黑椒漢堡，則不會在海洋公園、沙田馬場及跑馬地馬場的麥當勞分店出售。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2165000/2167508/20180924_mcd_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2165000%2F2167508%2F20180924_mcd_03_600.jpg&h=9dc7b436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍蝦湯味 Shake Shake 薯條亦會同步登場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2167508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2167508&d=bVbFEPqeSkte1NQq8Yo1ygCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b67eb515\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2167508</a>"},{"pid":"50ee9a6ef90e34f8633018a252a3461522c3c765","tid":834470,"uid":33359,"like":88,"dislike":3,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"爛屎漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1e2ccc8444a0b9ef579f8e8c915cf306c1dbf4","tid":834470,"uid":4420,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"龍蝦味薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e1cdee82ec2eb16ee393402be50ca25aabcaed","tid":834470,"uid":176304,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50ee9a6ef90e34f8633018a252a3461522c3c765","tid":834470,"uid":33359,"like":88,"dislike":3,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"爛屎漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好經典"},{"pid":"62a2b3f64e73c18e0bc986861a4178b0f73061b8","tid":834470,"uid":42804,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"加埋栗米脆片落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起啲畀黑椒汁整到栗米脆片淋哂寶係唔多開胃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9146902f65af7d98212b9fb2e78270fd923a32","tid":834470,"uid":1696,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"50ee9a6ef90e34f8633018a252a3461522c3c765","tid":834470,"uid":33359,"like":88,"dislike":3,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"爛屎漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a